  "page": "A Storm of Swords-Chapter 16",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background-color:rgb(35, 135, 75)\">Sansa II</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> chapter</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/A_storm_of_swords\" title=\"A storm of swords\"><img alt=\"AStormOfSwords.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/24/AStormOfSwords.jpg/220px-AStormOfSwords.jpg\" width=\"220\" height=\"353\" class=\"thumbborder\" srcset=\"/images/2/24/AStormOfSwords.jpg 1.5x\" /></a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">POV</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Sansa_Stark\" title=\"Sansa Stark\">Sansa</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Place</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Page</th><td>\n181 <small>UK HC</small> <small>(<a href=\"/index.php/Chapters_Table_of_contents\" title=\"Chapters Table of contents\">Other versions</a>)</small></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:rgb(35, 135, 75)\">Chapter chronology <small>(<a href=\"/index.php/Chapters\" title=\"Chapters\">All</a>)</small></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_6\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 6\">Sansa I</a><br />↑</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<table style=\"width:100%;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle;\"><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_15\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 15\">Jon II</a></td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:middle;\">&#160;←</td>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle; padding-right:0.1em; padding-left:0.1em;\"><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Sansa II</a></td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:middle;\">→&#160;</td>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle;\"><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_17\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 17\">Arya III</a></td>\n</tr></tbody></table></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n↓<br /><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_28\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 28\">Sansa III</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Synopsis\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Synopsis</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Character_List_appearing.2Fmentioned\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Character List appearing/mentioned</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Places_and_terms_mentioned\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Places and terms mentioned</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References_and_Notes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References and Notes</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Synopsis\">Synopsis</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_16&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Synopsis\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Sansa_Stark\" title=\"Sansa Stark\">Sansa</a> is being fitted for a new gown provided by Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Cersei_Lannister\" title=\"Cersei Lannister\">Cersei</a>. <a href=\"/index.php/Margaery_Tyrell\" title=\"Margaery Tyrell\">Margaery</a> tells Sansa that she does not fear <a href=\"/index.php/Joffrey_Baratheon\" title=\"Joffrey Baratheon\">Joffrey</a>, because <a href=\"/index.php/Mace_Tyrell\" title=\"Mace Tyrell\">her father</a> only conceded her hand in marriage with the provision that <a href=\"/index.php/Loras_Tyrell\" title=\"Loras Tyrell\">Loras</a> was named to the <a href=\"/index.php/Kingsguard\" title=\"Kingsguard\">Kingsguard</a>. Her brother will protect her from Joffrey. \n</p><p>When Sansa tells <a href=\"/index.php/Dontos_Hollard\" title=\"Dontos Hollard\">Dontos</a> about the <a href=\"/index.php/Olenna_Redwyne\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Olenna Redwyne\">Queen of Thorns</a>'s plan to marry her to <a href=\"/index.php/Willas_Tyrell\" title=\"Willas Tyrell\">Willas</a>, the drunk man warns her that the Tyrells wish to wed her for her claim to <a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=\"Winterfell\">Winterfell</a>, stating, \"These Tyrells are only <a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">Lannisters</a> with flowers.\" Dontos tells her that they will escape, as promised, on Joffrey's wedding day.\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"Character_List_appearing/mentioned\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Character_List_appearing.2Fmentioned\">Character List appearing/mentioned</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_16&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Character List appearing/mentioned\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"column-count:3; column-width:300px;\"> \n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Sansa_Stark\" title=\"Sansa Stark\">Sansa Stark</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Cersei_Lannister\" title=\"Cersei Lannister\">Cersei Lannister</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Margaery_Tyrell\" title=\"Margaery Tyrell\">Margaery Tyrell</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Joffrey_Baratheon\" title=\"Joffrey Baratheon\">Joffrey Baratheon</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Mace_Tyrell\" title=\"Mace Tyrell\">Mace Tyrell</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Loras_Tyrell\" title=\"Loras Tyrell\">Loras Tyrell</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Dontos_Hollard\" title=\"Dontos Hollard\">Dontos Hollard</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Olenna_Redwyne\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Olenna Redwyne\">Olenna Redwyne</a> Queen of Thornes</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Willas_Tyrell\" title=\"Willas Tyrell\">Willas Tyrell</a></li></ul>\n</div>\t\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Places_and_terms_mentioned\">Places and terms mentioned</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_16&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Places and terms mentioned\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"column-count:3; column-width:300px;\"> \n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Kingsguard\" title=\"Kingsguard\">Kingsguard</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=\"Winterfell\">Winterfell</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">House Lannister</a></li></ul>\n</div>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References_and_Notes\">References and Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_16&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References and Notes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>The synopsis was copied from AOL member vbkorik27 previously at <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external autonumber\" href=\"http://web.archive.org/web/20080228051425/members.aol.com/vbkorik27/summary/legend.html\">[1]</a>.</li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.tor.com/blogs/2012/11/a-read-of-ice-and-fire-a-storm-of-swords-part-9\">Summary and analysis</a> of the chapter upon a first read, by Leigh Butler</li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://slynt.blogspot.nl/2013/01/re-read-sansa-ii-growing-into-game.html\">Re-read: Sansa II, Growing into the Game</a>. Summary and analyses of the chapter in the course of a 10th reread by Slynt.</li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403192656\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.053 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.235 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 242/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 1104/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 7776/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1180/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.160/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 5.38 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  221.433      1 -total\n 99.37%  220.049      1 Template:Infobox_Chapter_ASoS\n 99.04%  219.298      1 Template:Infobox_Chapter\n 98.63%  218.401      1 Template:Infobox\n  0.52%    1.153      2 Template:Columns\n  0.46%    1.022      2 Template:Work_color\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:5761-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403192656 and revision id 241686\n -->\n",
